fields.name: AccountId
fields.description: The unique identifier associated with this Data Lake Analytics account.

fields.name: ComputePolicies
fields.description: The list of compute policies associated with this account.

fields.name: CreationTime
fields.description: The account creation time.

fields.name: CurrentTier
fields.description: The commitment tier in use for the current month.

fields.name: DataLakeStoreAccounts
fields.description: The list of Data Lake Store accounts associated with this account.

fields.name: DebugDataAccessLevel
fields.description: The current state of the DebugDataAccessLevel for this account.

fields.name: DefaultDataLakeStoreAccount
fields.description: The default Data Lake Store account associated with this account.

fields.name: Endpoint
fields.description: The full CName endpoint for this account.

fields.name: FirewallAllowAzureIPs
fields.description: The current state of allowing or disallowing IPs originating within Azure through the firewall. If the firewall is disabled, this is not enforced.

fields.name: FirewallRules
fields.description: The list of firewall rules associated with this account.

fields.name: FirewallState
fields.description: The current state of the IP address firewall for this account.

fields.name: HiveMetastores
fields.description: The list of hiveMetastores associated with this account.

fields.name: LastModifiedTime
fields.description: The account last modified time.

fields.name: MaxActiveJobCountPerUser
fields.description: The maximum supported active jobs under the account at the same time.

fields.name: MaxDegreeOfParallelism
fields.description: The maximum supported degree of parallelism for this account.

fields.name: MaxDegreeOfParallelismPerJob
fields.description: The maximum supported degree of parallelism per job for this account.

fields.name: MaxJobCount
fields.description: The maximum supported jobs running under the account at the same time.

fields.name: MaxJobRunningTimeInMin
fields.description: The maximum supported active jobs under the account at the same time.

fields.name: MaxQueuedJobCountPerUser
fields.description: The maximum supported jobs queued under the account at the same time.

fields.name: MinPriorityPerJob
fields.description: The minimum supported priority per job for this account.

fields.name: NewTier
fields.description: The commitment tier for the next month.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning status of the Data Lake Analytics account.

fields.name: PublicDataLakeStoreAccounts
fields.description: The list of Data Lake Store accounts associated with this account.

fields.name: QueryStoreRetention
fields.description: The number of days that job metadata is retained.

fields.name: State
fields.description: The state of the Data Lake Analytics account.

fields.name: StorageAccounts
fields.description: The list of Azure Blob Storage accounts associated with this account.

fields.name: SystemMaxDegreeOfParallelism
fields.description: The system defined maximum supported degree of parallelism for this account, which restricts the maximum value of parallelism the user can set for the account.

fields.name: SystemMaxJobCount
fields.description: The system defined maximum supported jobs running under the account at the same time, which restricts the maximum number of running jobs the user can set for the account.

fields.name: VirtualNetworkRules
fields.description: The list of virtualNetwork rules associated with this account.
